snippet.textDisplay:
I have so much to say. Words are just rushing and I can't get my thoughts straight but I'll try....

Dear Xulfi,

I want to extend my heartfelt gratitude for "Piya Piya Calling" from Coke Studio Pakistan Season 15. This song is a beautiful testament to the power of music in uniting diverse cultures and languages. The collaboration between artists like Kaifi Khalil, Chirag Rashmikant Patel, Amanda Delara, and Magdi Ytreeide, spanning languages such as Urdu, Norwegian, Gujarati, Arabic, and Punjabi, reflects a harmonious blend of voices and traditions that is truly inspiring.

Your vision and dedication in curating Coke Studio have created a platform where art transcends boundaries. It’s a place where there is no room for hatred, only admiration and respect for each other's craft. Through your work, you’ve not only brought the world closer but also showcased the richness of Pakistani culture to a global audience. 

Thank you for fostering a space that celebrates love, warmth, and connection. Coke Studio stands as a beacon of hope, promoting unity and cultural appreciation. 

With deepest admiration,

Fan from the very beginning of coke studio

Salman......
